Game of Thrones‘ series finale trailer has been as crucially anticipated as the entire season in itself. The penultimate episode of not just the season, but the entire series aired on HBO last weekend where we saw Daenerys Targaryen (Emilia Clarke) successfully defeat Cersei Lannister and overtake King’s Landing, Shockingly, Targaryen did this in a much more forceful way than originally planned, leaving plenty of ashes and casualties in what she believes to be her new kingdom. This sets up the series finale to see how the world and the remaining characters respond to her actions. In order to reduce the pressures of what the last episode holds, here’s a sneak-peek: 